---
title: Extra
---

<div id="extra" class="row">
  <div class="extra-container col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12">
    <div class="heading"><%= current_page.data.title %></div>
    <div class="intro">
      Come ogni anno Tendenze Festival vi propone un percorso attraverso il meglio dell'extra alternativo ed innovativo, tra artigianato, vintage, musica, creativit√† e associazionismo in tutte le sue forme.
      <br/>
      <strong>La lista e le schede sono in continuo aggiornamento!</strong>
    </div>
    <% get_md_files("data/extra").each do |name| %>
    <% data = get_data("extra", name) %>
    <div class="exhibitor row">
      <div class="name col-xs-12 visible-xs"><%= data["name"] %></div>
      <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-3 col-md-3">
        <div class="image">
          <%= image_tag data['thumbnail'], :class => "img-responsive" %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="content col-xs-12 col-sm-9 col-md-9">
        <div class="name hidden-xs"><%= data["name"] %></div>
        <div class="text"><%= data["text"] %></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
